Document: MultiplayerAPIExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_multiplayerapiextension.rst
Summary: Defines the methods that can be overridden to extend the MultiplayerAPI functionality.

Methods
- _get_multiplayer_peer() -> MultiplayerPeer: virtual. Called when the MultiplayerAPI.multiplayer_peer is retrieved.
- _get_peer_ids() -> PackedInt32Array: virtual, const. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.get_peers().
- _get_remote_sender_id() -> int: virtual, const. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.get_remote_sender_id().
- _get_unique_id() -> int: virtual, const. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.get_unique_id().
- _object_configuration_add(object: Object, configuration: Variant) -> Error: virtual. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.object_configuration_add().
- _object_configuration_remove(object: Object, configuration: Variant) -> Error: virtual. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.object_configuration_remove().
- _poll() -> Error: virtual. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.poll().
- _rpc(peer: int, object: Object, method: StringName, args: Array) -> Error: virtual. Callback for MultiplayerAPI.rpc().
- _set_multiplayer_peer(multiplayer_peer: MultiplayerPeer) -> void: virtual. Called when the MultiplayerAPI.multiplayer_peer is set.